pageTitle: Bike and Hike is Saturday | LebanonEnterprise.com
TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {28369=The Marion County Fitness and Nutrition Coalition is hosting its annual Family Bike and Hike 5K Run/Walk Saturday, April 20 at Graham Memorial Park. The Family Bike and Hike is open to everyone in the community, although parents must accompany their children during this event. Children 5 and under can participate for free, but they must be registered for the event. Registration the day of the event will begin at 8 a.m. at the girls softball pavilion. The 10K bike will begin at 9 a.m., and the 5K run/walk will begin at 9:15 a.m. Prizes will also be awarded for 5K participants in various categories. All participants will receive breakfast, a t-shirt and goody bag, and they will be eligible for door prizes. For more information, call (270) 692-3393 or 699-3906., 37157=Copyright © 2015}
